# switchtest

`switchtest` is a Python CLI for running SSH-based functional tests against network switches using declarative YAML test definitions.

## Quick start

```powershell
venv\Scripts\python.exe -m pip install -e .[dev]
venv\Scripts\switchtest --help
venv\Scripts\pytest
```
